TI  - With Friends Like These Endogenous Labor Market Segregation with Homogeneous, Nonprejudiced Agents
T2  - AMERICAN JOURNAL OF ECONOMICS AND SOCIOLOGY
KW  - SOCIAL NETWORKS
KW  - MODEL
KW  - DISCRIMINATION
