TI  - Social networks, job search methods and reservation wages: evidence for Germany
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF MANPOWER
KW  - Job search behaviour
KW  - Unemployment
KW  - Social networks
KW  - Germany
KW  - Jobs
KW  - LABOR-MARKET OUTCOMES
