TI  - Gender-specific effects of commuting and relocation on a couple's social life
T2  - DEMOGRAPHIC RESEARCH
KW  - FAMILY MIGRATION
KW  - WOMEN
KW  - WORK
KW  - MEN
KW  - DETERMINANTS
