TI  - The antecedents and consequences of employees' followership behavior in social network organizational context: a longitudinal study
T2  - EURASIP JOURNAL ON WIRELESS COMMUNICATIONS AND NETWORKING
KW  - Social network
KW  - Personality preference
KW  - Regulatory focus theory
KW  - Political skills
