TI  - Pandemic silver lining: how the COVID-19 pandemic helped women to beat the "gender stereotypes pandemic" in entrepreneurship
T2  - GENDER IN MANAGEMENT
KW  - COVID-19
KW  - Women entrepreneurship
KW  - Occupational gender stereotypes
KW  - Social networks
KW  - Turkey
KW  - ECONOMIC-CRISIS
