TI  - Research on the spatial spillover effect of high-speed railway on the income of urban residents in China
T2  - HUMANITIES & SOCIAL SCIENCES COMMUNICATIONS
KW  - TRANSPORTATION INFRASTRUCTURE
KW  - ACCESSIBILITY
KW  - PRODUCTIVITY
KW  - ECONOMY
