TI  - "I am like a deaf, dumb and blind person": Mobility and immobility of Chinese (im)migrants in Flushing, Queens, New York City
T2  - JOURNAL OF TRANSPORT GEOGRAPHY
KW  - SOCIAL EXCLUSION
