TI  - A multidimensional network link prediction algorithm and its application for predicting social relationships
T2  - JOURNAL OF COMPUTATIONAL SCIENCE
KW  - Multidimensional network model
KW  - Link prediction
KW  - Social relationship
KW  - Superedge similarity
KW  - Polygonal structure
