TI  - Teleworkers with disabilities: Characteristics and accommodation use
T2  - WORK-A JOURNAL OF PREVENTION ASSESSMENT & REHABILITATION
KW  - Employment
KW  - workplace accommodations
KW  - remote work
KW  - work environment
